text: Corvallis is a city in the U.S. state of Oregon. Corvallis is the location of Oregon State University.Corvallis Convention & Visitors Bureau As of 2020, the population was 59,922. It is the county seat of Benton County, as well as the most populated city in Benton County. ==References== Category:Cities in Oregon Category:County seats in Oregon
title: Corvallis, Oregon
